; Slow 1100mV 85C Model Fmax Summary              ;
+-----------+-----------------+------------+------+
; Fmax      ; Restricted Fmax ; Clock Name ; Note ;
+-----------+-----------------+------------+------+
; 71.83 MHz ; 71.83 MHz       ; clk        ;      ;
